
Feature 4: Task Continuity & Reminder System

This feature ensures open tasks are carried forward and responsible individuals are reminded before meetings.

Epic 4.1: Carry Forward Open Tasks

Open agenda points should continue into future meetings until completed.

User Stories:

Automatic Carry Forward: As a user, I want open agenda points from the previous meeting to automatically appear in the next meeting so that unfinished work is not lost.

View Carried Forward Tasks: As a user, I want to see tasks carried forward from previous meetings to track pending work.

Confirm/Remove Tasks: As a user, I want to confirm or remove carried-forward tasks when creating a new meeting to keep agendas relevant.

Epic 4.2: WhatsApp Reminder System

Responsible members need timely reminders for pending tasks.

User Stories:

Detect Open Tasks: As a user, I want the system to detect open agenda points before the next meeting so that reminders can be sent automatically.

Send WhatsApp Reminder: As a responsible person, I want to receive a WhatsApp reminder for open tasks so that I remember to complete them.

Include Task & Meeting Info: As a user, I want the reminder message to include the task description and meeting date so that the recipient clearly understands the pending work.